      "description": "Five-fold cross-validation was performed on the full nominal dataset to assess generalization within the training distribution. Mean cross-validated MAE = 0.034 ± 0.006. All folds produced predictions within the RH < 1 acceptance band. No out-of-distribution, shifted, or perturbed conditions were included in any fold.",
      "metric": "Cross-validated MAE = 0.034 ± 0.006",
      "passFailStatus": "Pass"
