      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled ML training pipeline with documented dependencies and reproducible training runs.",
      "rationale": "The ML surrogate training pipeline is managed under version control (Git). Dependency environments are pinned via a requirements manifest. Training runs are logged with fixed random seeds ensuring reproducibility. SQA documentation meets MRL 2 requirements."
