    "rationale": "The ML surrogate model for CPB hemolysis prediction meets all required credibility factor levels at MRL 2 for the nominal operating envelope. All 13 credibility factors have been assessed or scoped appropriately. Nominal test-set MAE (0.031) and R² (0.964) satisfy the acceptance criteria. All validation comparisons against CFD reference and bench measurements fall within the 5% tolerance band. The model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions within the nominal CPB operating envelope as defined in the COU.",
